<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>Welcome to Kyn</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style type="text/css">
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        background-color: #fafafa;
        color: #222222;
      }

      a {
        color: #000;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.25;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      p {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      table td {
        vertical-align: top;
      }

      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .email-header {
        background-color: #0070f3;
        padding: 24px;
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      .email-body {
        padding: 24px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
      }

      .email-footer {
        background-color: #f6f6f6;
        padding: 24px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #0070f3;
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-align: center;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="email-header">
        <h1>Welcome to Kyn 👋</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="email-body">
        <p>Dear <%=fullname%>,</p>

        <p>
          We're thrilled to welcome you to <strong>Kyn</strong>! We appreciate
          your trust in us and are excited to help you manage your wallet and
          make an impact in the world through kindness.
        </p>

        <p>
          Your account has been successfully created. Below are your details:
        </p>

        <p><strong>Name:</strong> <%=fullname%></p>
        <p><strong>Kyn Tag:</strong> <%=KynTag%></p>

        <p><strong>To begin:</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            Go to our website or download the Kyn mobile app from the App Store
            or Google Play.
          </li>
          <li>Click the <strong>"Log In"</strong> button and sign in.</li>
          <li>
            Once logged in, you'll be able to send and receive help, view your
            balance, earn Kyn points, and more.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          If you have any questions, our friendly support team is available 24/7
          via chat, email, or phone. We're here to ensure your experience is
          seamless and rewarding.
        </p>

        <p>
          Thank you again for choosing <strong>Kyn</strong> as your partner in
          doing good.
        </p>

        <p>Warm regards,<br />— The Kyn Team</p>
      </div>

      <div class="email-footer">
        <p>
          Need help? Contact us at
          <a href="mailto:kyn.value@gmail.com"
            >christopherockyn.valuehe827@gmail.com</a
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
